en_646040_0	A new accommodation block, constructed within a short period for the benefit of Other Ranks serving the Security Force Headquarters - East (SFHQ-E) at Welikanda was vested in the soldiers by the Commander of the Army, Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake who was in the East in connection with a series of other events during the weekend (30 - 31 March).
en_646040_1	This new accommodation complex was constructed by the troops of Corps of Engineer Services (CES), headed by Captain V.H.G.N.R Janasinghe, the Garrison Engineer, Welikanda under the guidance of Major General Aruna Jayasekera, Commander, Security Forces - East and senior Officers in the SFHQ-E.
